## ğŸ“¦ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AmirJT/get-better-journal.git
cd get-better-journal
```

### ğŸ”§ Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start
```

Make sure your `.env` file in `/backend` includes:

```env
MONGO_URI=your_mongo_uri
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
PORT=8000
```

### ğŸ’» Frontend

```bash
cd ../frontend
npm install
